public boolean compressFile(java.lang.String inputFile,
                            java.lang.String outputFile,
                            boolean keepOriginal)
This procedure compresses a file to the .gz or .gzip zip format and may retain or delete the original uncompressed file.

Parameters:
inputFile - The complete path to the file we wish to decompress
outputFile - The complete path to where we wish to store the uncompressed file
keepCompressed - Whether to retain the original compressed file
Returns:
A boolean value indicating success or failure of the decompression
